#Terraform code to create telegraf instances
#run boot-up script to install telegraf

Steps to create apache instances :
1. Create a new user with the right IAM access and generate keys
2. Update the secrets.tfvars file with the keys generated in step 2
3. Ensure the right key-pair is used
4. Make sure terrform is installed on your local machine and is set in your path
5. Update variables.tf in telegraf folder
5. run the terraform script :
   $ ./terraform.sh

Steps to destroy apache instances :
1. Run the terraform destroy script :
   $ ./terraform-destroy.sh
